        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "New on TRENDYGOLF: Rhone Women's Golfwear Has Arrived",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At TRENDYGOLF, we're always looking to bring in brands that blend performance with style and Rhone has officially entered the chat.</p><p>Already a standout in the men's space, Rhone is known for designing elevated activewear that fits seamlessly into real life. Now, they've expanded into women's golf apparel, and let's just say… it was worth the wait. Their debut women's collection is all about versatile silhouettes, premium fabrications, and understated style that still feels special.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_1",
        "text_1"
      ],
