    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "A Brand That Gets It",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Golfwear has come a long way, and Rhone is helping push it even further. Their pieces are tailored without being tight, athletic without being overbuilt, and stylish without trying too hard. Every item is designed to perform on the course but still feel great when you're grabbing coffee, heading to the gym, or just living your life. It's modern minimalism, made for movement.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
