    "text_3": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Golf Clothes That Don't Scream \"Golf Clothes\"",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>One of the best things about Rhone's women's line? You don't have to be on the course to wear it. Sure, these pieces are designed to handle 18 holes in the sun but they're also perfect for running errands, hopping on a Zoom call, or squeezing in a Pilates class. They're transitional, elevated, and totally re-wearable.</p><p>The fabrics are breathable and lightweight with just the right amount of stretch, and the cuts are easy without being basic. Think: golf wear you'll actually want to wear off the course.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_1",
        "text_1"
