          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Why Rhone Fits the TRENDYGOLF Edit",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We've always been about brands that raise the bar. Rhone is one of those brands. They've taken everything that works about performance wear and combined it with a thoughtful, style-forward perspective. It's clean. It's cool. It's made for the modern woman who moves through a lot of different spaces and wants her clothes to keep up.</p>"
          }
        }
